articles.title: UK's Sunak sees off revolt to win vote on Rwanda migrant plan - Reuters UK
articles.description: British Prime Minister Rishi Sunak avoided defeat in parliament on Tuesday on an emergency bill to revive his plan to send asylum seekers to Rwanda, seeing off a revolt by dozens of his lawmakers that laid bare his party's deep divisions.
